high_descs: Walk straight and turn left to reach the coffeetable.
Take a butterknife from the top of the tea table.
Left turn and immediately take a right turn and again take a right turn to reach the side of the apple tea table.
Cut a green apple into pieces which is kept on the table.
Take a left turn and walk straight to reach the fridge on the right side.
Open the butterknife cabin, put the butterknife inside the fridge cabin and close the fridge cabin.
Turn towards right and walk straight and again take a left turn to reach the coffeetable.
Take a piece of cut apple from the table.
Turn left and walk straight and turn right to reach the fridge again.
Open the cabin the put the piece of apple inside the cabin and close the cabin. After few seconds open the cabin and take the apple out of the cabin and close the door.
Turn left and walk few steps and again turn left to reach the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the apple piece inside it and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple in the microwave

high_descs: walk to the coffeetable
pick up butterknife from the table
walk around to the other side of the apple.
Cut the apple into slices.
walk with knife to the fridge
Place the butterknife inside the fridge.
walk back to the coffeetable
pick up the apple from the table
walk to fridge with slice of apple
Place the apple into storage.
take apple back out and walk to the microwave
Place the slice of apple into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Get a slice of apple and put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Go forward to the white coffeetable.
Pick up the butterknife from the table.
Turn left and go to the side of the apple.
Slice the green apple on the table.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the butterknife in the fridge.
Turn right and go back to the coffeetable.
Pick up a green apple slice from the table.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Place the apple slice in the fridge, close the fridge and then take the apple slice from the fridge.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Place the apple slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place an apple slice in the microwave.
